message: Dear Bob, I am excited to present our premium product, which is tailored to meet your specific needs and valued at $12000. Considering its high quality and the benefits it offers, I am extending an exclusive opportunity for you to acquire it at a special introductory price of $11000. This is a limited-time offer, so I encourage you to respond promptly to secure this exceptional deal. Thank you for considering our product, and I look forward to your positive response.
